#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 146. Nibbidābahulasutta → kulaputtena dukkhā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.146:0.3"
msgid "146. Nibbidābahulasutta "
msgstr "146. Full of Disillusionment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.146:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.146:1.2"
msgid "“Saddhāpabbajitassa, bhikkhave, kulaputtassa ayamanudhammo hoti—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, when a gentleman has gone forth out of faith, this is what’s in line with the teachings. "

#. VAR: nibbidābahulo → nibbidābahulaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn22.146:1.3"
msgid "yaṃ rūpe nibbidābahulo vihareyya. Vedanāya … pe … saññāya … saṅkhāresu … viññāṇe nibbidābahulo vihareyya. "
msgstr "They should live full of disillusionment for form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.146:1.4"
msgid "Yo rūpe nibbidābahulo viharanto, vedanāya … saññāya … saṅkhāresu … viññāṇe nibbidābahulo viharanto rūpaṃ parijānāti, vedanaṃ … saññaṃ … saṅkhāre … viññāṇaṃ parijānāti; "
msgstr "Living in this way, they completely understand form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.146:1.5"
msgid "so rūpaṃ parijānaṃ vedanaṃ parijānaṃ saññaṃ parijānaṃ saṅkhāre parijānaṃ viññāṇaṃ parijānaṃ parimuccati rūpamhā, parimuccati vedanāya, parimuccati saññāya, parimuccati saṅkhārehi, parimuccati viññāṇamhā, parimuccati jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi; ‘parimuccati dukkhasmā’ti vadāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Completely understanding form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness, they’re freed from these things. They’re freed from rebirth, old age, and death, from sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. They’re freed from suffering, I say.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.146:1.6"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

